data.description: 1990s manufactured home on 4 Tranquil Acres near Fredericksburg, Texas.  Tucked away Just outside of Fredericksburg, this 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home offers a comfortable blend of rustic charm and modern convenience. Set on a spacious 4-acre lot, this property is perfect for those seeking a quiet, secure, and simple rural lifestyle while still being only minutes away from the lively town of Fredericksburg.  Perfect for a few animals a garden, or for a family with kids in 4H to keep and work with their projects.
